		<hr />
		
		
		
		
		<div>The reason why this cannot be done is that windows are opened by the servers, not the XML files. The XML files only determine what the layouts of the windows look like -- nothing more.<br />
<br />
Sadly, there's not much that can be done about this on our end. In order for anything like this to be done, Verant would need to create the functionality for custom windows on the servers. Until then, we can only re-write existing windows.</div>
	</td>
</tr>
</table>
